data.text:
Requeijao Light Quata 180g is backordered and will ship as soon as it is back in stock.

Light, healthy and a source of calcium, the Light Cheese Cream is the delicious news to spread around. Bringing all the benefits of cheese to the 180g cup format, Light Cheese Cream has 25% less total fat, making it a great option to start the day in a lighter way, combined with a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Minas Frescal cheese (pasteurized milk, calcium chloride, sodium chloride, lactic acid acidity regulator and chymosin coagulant), Fresh ricotta (whey, pasteurized skimmed milk, calcium chloride), Cream, Pasta for processed dairy product (pasteurized skimmed milk and lactic yeast), Modified starch, Tricalcium phosphate, Sodium chloride, Emulsifiers: tetrasodium pyrophosphate and sodium polyphosphate, Lactic acid acidity regulator, Thickeners: guar gum and xanthan gum, Preservatives potassium sorbate and nisin. GLUTEN-FREE. ALLERGENS: CONTAINS MILK AND DERIVATIVES. CONTAINS LACTOSE.

Amount per serving

Serving Size 30g (1 and 1/2 tablespoon)

%DV (*) Energetic value 66kcal = 278kJ 3 carbohydrates 1.2g 0 Proteins 4.1g 5 Total fat 5.0g 9 Saturated fat 3.0g 14 trans fats 0 ** dietary fiber 0 0 Sodium 96mg 11 Calcium 105mg 4

(*) % Daily reference values ​​based on a 2000 kcal diet. Your Daily Values ​​may be higher or lower depending on your energy needs.
